tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (The bank is open for Lonzo Ball) 2021/2/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: The bank is open for Lonzo Ball

videos.description: Zion Williamson doesn't let contact from Daniel Theis stop him from getting the layup to fall.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zion powers through contact from Theis for and-1) 2021/2/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion powers through contact from Theis for and-1

videos.description: Jaylen Brown tosses up the perfect lob to Robert Williams III for the two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Robert Williams reaches new heights to catch the lob from Brown) 2021/2/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robert Williams reaches new heights to catch the lob from Brown

videos.description: Jayson Tatum takes advantage of the Pelicans' turnover with a rim-rocking jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum takes flight for breakaway slam) 2021/2/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum takes flight for breakaway slam

videos.description: Jayson Tatum goes into his bag of tricks to shake off Nickeil Alexander-Walker for the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum gets fancy with his dribble to get the 3-pointer off) 2021/2/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum gets fancy with his dribble to get the 3-pointer off

videos.description: Jaylen Brown connects with Robert Williams III for a huge thunderous slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Robert Williams skies for alley-oop throwdown) 2021/2/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robert Williams skies for alley-oop throwdown

videos.description: Zion Williamson goes coast-to-coast for a layup to beat the third-quarter buzzer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zion floats by Thompson to beat the buzzer) 2021/2/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion floats by Thompson to beat the buzzer

videos.description: JJ Redick puts a side spin on the ball as he passes it to the referee and receives his second technical foul, earning him an ejection from the game.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (JJ Redick gets ejected from game after exchange with ref) 2021/2/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: JJ Redick gets ejected from game after exchange with ref

videos.description: Lonzo Ball tosses inside to Zion Williamson, who gets a tough layup to fall over Jaylen Brown.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zion hyped after outmuscling Brown for a layup) 2021/2/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion hyped after outmuscling Brown for a layup

videos.description: Jayson Tatum goes head-to-head with Josh Hart and shows off his elite footwork before knocking down the shot.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum spins on Hart for a basket) 2021/2/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum spins on Hart for a basket

videos.description: Zion Williamson powers through Tristan Thompson for the go-ahead layup. On the next possession, with time winding down, Jayson Tatum drives and floats in the shot over Josh Hart to tie it up.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zion, Tatum trade clutch baskets late) 2021/2/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion, Tatum trade clutch baskets late

videos.description: Robert Williams III meets Zion Williamson at the basket with a big block.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Robert Williams emphatically blocks Zion) 2021/2/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robert Williams emphatically blocks Zion

videos.description: Zion Williamson drives into traffic and kicks out to Brandon Ingram for the clutch 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Ingram confidently drains go-ahead 3-pointer

videos.description: Zion Williamson and Brandon Ingram combine for 61 points as the Pelicans erase a 24-point deficit to defeat the Celtics in overtime 120-115.
